        "Sync errors"
      ],
      "priority": 1,
      "url": "https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/troubleshoot/exchange/client-connectivity/ost-sync-issues",
      "steps": [
        "Close Outlook completely.",
        {
          "text": "Locate OST: File > Account Settings > Data Files tab.",
          "image": "assets/images/ost-location.svg",
          "alt": "OST file location",
          "platforms": [
            "Windows"
          ]
        },
        "Rename the .ost file (e.g. add .old) — do not delete if you have unsynced local-only data.",
        "Restart Outlook — a new OST will download from Exchange Online.",
        {
          "text": "Wait for initial sync to complete (time varies by mailbox size).",
          "tip": "Large mailboxes may take hours on first sync."
        }
      ]
    },
